#: spack.util.compression.extension_from_magic_numbers:10
msgid ""
"Spack recognized archive file extension as determined by file's magic number "
"and file name. If file is not on system or is of a type not recognized by "
"Spack as an archive or compression type, None is returned. If the file is "
"classified as a compressed tarball, the extension is abbreviated (for "
"instance ``tgz`` not ``tar.gz``) if that matches the file's given extension."
msgstr ""

